"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-TeXmathchoice"><span class="mjx-mstyle"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">(</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.6em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 0.6em; top: -1.144em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 0.6em; bottom: -0.711em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span><span style="height: 1.854em; vertical-align: -0.711em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-TeXmathchoice"><span class="mjx-mstyle"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">×</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.578em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 1.578em; top: -1.368em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 1.578em; bottom: -0.767em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">m</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.578em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.135em; vertical-align: -0.767em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">∼</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.578em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 1.578em; top: -1.528em;"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 1.578em; bottom: -0.778em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">4</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">m</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.578em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.306em; vertical-align: -0.778em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span>最后形成多语义神经元。</p><h3>实验</h3><p>训练我们在<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n \ce 256"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">: <span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.314em;">=</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">256</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="m"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">m</span></span></span></span></span></span>范围从<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="256"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">256</span></span></span></span></span></span>到<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="4096"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">4096</span></span></span></span></span></span>上描述的模型表明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Theta\P{\f{n^2}{m}}"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="width: 3.102em;" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">θ</span></span></span></span></span></span>的这种趋势<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Theta\P{\f{n^2}{m}}"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="width: 3.102em;" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mspace" style="margin-right: -0.167em; width: 0px; height: 0px;"></span><span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size2-R" style="padding-top: 0.961em; padding-bottom: 0.961em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.89em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.258em; top: -1.631em;"><span class="mjx-msubsup" style=""><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.435em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.258em; bottom: -0.524em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">米</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.89em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.524em; vertical-align: -0.37em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size2-R" style="padding-top: 0.961em; padding-bottom: 0.961em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>成立，常数<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\f14"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.495em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.7em; top: -1.372em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.7em; bottom: -0.676em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">4</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.495em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.449em; vertical-align: -0.478em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span>似乎也相当准确。 </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/sEyWufriufTnBKnTG/yfkj4dw0uqjggzpsfvhb" alt=""></p><h2>讨论和未来的工作</h2><h3>对机械解释的影响</h3><p>多义性有两种完全不同的发生方式，这一事实可能会对如何处理它产生重要影响。</p><p>据我们所知，多语义性主要在编码空间没有特权基础的环境中进行研究：空间可以任意旋转<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="l_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">而不</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>改变动态，特别是相应的层不具有非线性或除 l 之外的任何正则化<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="l_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> .在这种设置下，特征可以在编码空间中任意表示，并且通常仅当特征多于维度时我们才会观察到干扰（非正交编码）。</p><p>另一方面，我们在这里演示的附带多语义性本质上与规范基础相关，取决于随机初始化和动态，甚至当可用维度明显多于特征时也会发生。</p><p>这意味着某些针对一种多语义的工具可能不适用于另一种多语义。例如：</p><ul><li>当存在非线性时，对编码的线性结构做出假设的工具可能无法正常工作。</li><li>在没有特权基础的情况下，摆脱叠加的一种成本高昂但技术上可行的方法是仅增加神经元的数量，使其与特征的数量相匹配。以这种方式消除偶然的多语义性是不太现实的，因为我们看到它可能会发生，直到神经元的数量大致等于特征数量的<em>平方</em>。</li><li>另一方面，由于附带多语义性取决于随机初始化和训练动态，因此可以通过以各种方式推动学习轨迹来解决它，而不必改变神经架构的任何内容。<ul><li>举个例子，这是一种可能的方法，可以消除当前代表两个特征<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span>的神经元中的偶然多语义性。复制该神经元，将其传出权重除以<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span> （这样就不会影响下游层），向每个副本的传入权重添加少量噪声，然后再运行几个步骤的梯度下降。人们可能希望这会导致副本彼此分离，其中一个副本最终获得特征<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span>的完全所有权，而另一个副本获得特征<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span>的完全所有权。</li></ul></li></ul><p>此外，找到区分偶然多义性和必要多义性的方法也是很有趣的。</p><ul><li>我们是否可以仅根据模型的最终训练状态来区分它们，或者我们是否需要更多地了解训练期间发生的情况？</li><li>现实世界神经网络中的“大部分”多义性是必要的还是偶然的？这如何取决于架构和数据？</li></ul><h3>更真实的玩具模型</h3><p>我们研究的设置在几个方面都很简单。其中一些方法不失（很多）通用性，例如编码和解码矩阵捆绑在一起的事实， <sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-9" id="fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-9">[9]</a></sup>或输入特征是基向量的事实。 <sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-10" id="fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-10">[10]</a></sup></p><p>但为了简单起见，我们也做出了一些选择，这些选择可能更重要，并且最好进行研究。尤其：</p><ul><li>我们使用<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="l_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">l</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>正则化引入了赢家通吃的动态。这使得稀疏化的研究相当不错，但<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="l_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">l</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>正则化并不是很常用，也不是现代神经网络中特权基的主要原因。研究因不同原因（例如非线性激活函数或层归一化）而发生的赢家通吃动态并查看稀疏化的动态是否相似会很有趣。</li><li>在我们的设置中，多语义性是良性的，因为一个特征可以用正激活表示，另一个特征可以用负激活表示，并且输出层中的 ReLU 消除了歧义。由于其他原因，多语义性可能是良性的：例如，两个特征可能永远不会出现在同一上下文中，并且上下文可用于消除它们之间的歧义。我们在<a href="https://victorlecomte.com/notes/disambiguation-by-another-feature">工作说明</a>中给出了这种情况下可能的玩具模型。</li></ul><h3>理论中的差距</h3><p>通过考虑忽略干扰时特征受益力和正则化如何相互作用，我们能够为稀疏化过程提供强有力的理论保证，但我们还无法对这三种力如何相互作用做出自信的理论主张。</p><p>尤其：</p><ul><li>从理论上预测<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="W_i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.104em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.104em;">W</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>中的最大坐标在整个训练过程中保持最大的可能性会很好。这需要更好地理解当所涉及的权重之一明显大于另一个权重时，恶意冲突的影响到底有多大，以及这对编码中最大权重之间的竞争有多大影响。</li><li>也许一个有趣的研究案例是极限<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda \to 0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">→</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span> （非常慢的正则化）。这将使干扰工作比正则化快得多，并且从研究稀疏化的角度来看，这可以让我们假设内积<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="W_i \cdot W_j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.104em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.104em;">W</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.104em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.104em;">W</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>在整个训练过程中都是非正的。</li></ul><h2>作者贡献</h2><ul><li>构想：Victor 最初提出了这个项目，并在与 Rylan 的讨论中成形。</li><li>实验：Kushal 和 Trevor 进行的实验证实了偶然多义性的发生，并测量了多义神经元的数量。他们受到维克多和瑞兰的指导。</li><li>理论：Victor 在 Kushal 的大力帮助下推动了理论工作并实现了稀疏化的数值模拟。</li><li>写作：这篇文章主要由 Victor 撰写，并得到了 Kushal 和 Rylan 的反馈。 </li></ul><hr class="footnotes-sep"><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-1" class="footnote-item"><p>例如，参见<a href="https://distill.pub/2020/circuits/zoom-in/#claim-1-polysemantic">放大：电路简介</a>中的“多语义神经元”部分<a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-2" class="footnote-item"><p>当我们说神经元与特征相关时，更正式的意思是神经元的激活与输入中是否存在该特征相关（其中相关性针对数据点）。但前者说起来更容易。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-2" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-3" class="footnote-item"><p>类似的现象还有其他名称，例如“特权基础”。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-3" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-4" class="footnote-item"><p>主要取决于神经架构和数据的具体情况（也取决于权重的随机初始化） <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-4" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-5" class="footnote-item"><p>在这里，我们将“碰撞”定义为两个特征<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span>碰撞的事件。例如， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span> 、 <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="k"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span></span></span></span></span>之间存在三向碰撞，这将算作<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span> 、 <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="k"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span></span></span></span></span>以及<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="j"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="k"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span></span></span></span></span>之间的三次碰撞。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-5" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-6" class="footnote-item"><p>我们使用<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\norm{\cdot}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">∥</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">∥</span></span></span></span></span></span>表示欧几里得长度（ <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="l_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">l</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>范数），使用<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\norm{\cdot}_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">∥</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">∥</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>表示曼哈顿长度（ <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="l_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">l</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>范数）。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-6" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-7" class="footnote-item"><p>这相当于使<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span>变大四倍，并使训练时间变慢四倍。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-7" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-8" class="footnote-item"><p>这不一定是初始化时的最大权重，因为可能与其他编码存在重大冲突，但考虑到所有因素，初始化时的最大权重仍然是最有可能赢得比赛的。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-8" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-9" class="footnote-item"><p>我们指的是编码矩阵<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="W\t"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.104em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.104em;">W</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.262em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-sans-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">T</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>被迫成为解码矩阵<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="W"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.104em;">W</span></span></span></span></span></span>的转置的事实。这个假设是有道理的，因为即使它们保持独立并初始化为不同的值，由于学习动态，它们随着时间的推移自然会获得相似的值。事实上，编码矩阵的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i\th"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">第</span></span></span><span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">i</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">列</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和解码矩阵的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i\th"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">第</span></span></span><span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">i</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">行</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>通过特征受益力“相互增强”，直到它们的内积为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，并且只要它们一开始很小或如果存在一些重量衰减，那么在训练结束时它们将几乎相同。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-9" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-10" class="footnote-item"><p>如果输入特征不是规范基向量但仍然是正交的（并且输出仍然是基向量），那么我们可以对编码矩阵应用固定的线性变换并恢复相同的训练动态。一般来说，考虑正交输入特征是有意义的，因为当特征本身不正交（或至少近似正交）时，什么是多语义性的问题就变得更加模糊。 <a href="#fnref-7ZDJE8KovauHeeNeH-10" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section><br/><br/><a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/sEyWufriufTnBKnTG/incidental-polysemanticity#comments">讨论</a>; https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/sEyWufriufTnBKnTG/incidental-polysemanticity塞乌弗里夫TnBKntGVictor Lecomte Wed, 15 Nov 2023 04:00:00 GMT 
LLMs May Find It Hard to FOOMPublished on November 15, 2023 2:52 AM GMT<br/><br/><p><i>认知状态：其中的一些技术进步部分我已经思考了很多年，其他更多的法学硕士特定部分我已经思考了几个月或几天。</i></p><p> LLM 被训练为令牌生成过程的<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/vJFdjigzmcXMhNTsx/simulators">模拟器</a>，其（在任何源自互联网的训练集中）通常是类人或人类衍生的代理。这些模拟代理的计算能力受法学硕士的前向计算能力的限制，但不受以下限制。一个非常大的法学硕士可以而且经常会对一个非常普通的人进行极其准确的描绘：一个足够强大的法学硕士在模拟智商大约为 100 的普通人类的任务中可能是非常超人的，比任何人类都好得多作家或即兴演员——但无论它模拟的普通人都不会是超人，而且这种能力也不是制造<a href="https://old-wiki.lesswrong.com/w/index.php?title=AI_takeoff&amp;_ga=2.195370917.803104956.1699518808-685953086.1699518806#Hard_takeoff">FOOM</a>的材料。</p><p>假设我们有一个法学硕士，其架构和规模在计算上能够在一次前向传递中对智商为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="O(1000)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">O</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1000</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的人类进行良好的模拟<style>.mjx-chtml {display: inline-block; line-height: 0; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 100%; font-size-adjust: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; word-spacing: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 1px 0}
